text: Fibs (stylised in all caps as FIBS) is the second full-length studio album by the British composer and electronica musician Anna Meredith, released on 25 October 2019 on Moshi Moshi. It was nominated for the 2020 Mercury Prize. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2019 albums Category:Anna Meredith albums
title: Fibs (album)
